    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potato[es] is in the microwave, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
