    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel <strong>half</strong> your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Grate the <strong>remaining Italian hard cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
