            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>trimmed</strong> <strong>green beans</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil </strong>(or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and a very small knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the green beans to form a tightly sealed parcel[s] and add to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until the green beans are tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-4-1688738029077-x200.jpg",
