          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-4-1688738029077-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato has had an initial 15-16 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and carefully slice in half down the middle (careful, it will be hot!)</p><p>Spoon the <strong>homemade cheesy beans</strong> over your baked potato[es] and top with the<strong> torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 7-8 min or until melted and oozy – this is your <strong>jacket potato with homemade cheesy beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
