          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-4-1688738032673-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-4-1688738032673-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> jacket potato with homemade cheesy beans</strong> with the<strong> green beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> Italian hard cheese shavings</strong> over the beans and season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the cheese shavings and black pepper!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
